g.text: In this workflow we convert raw customer transactions, i.e. contract registrations, into money measures on the one hand and loyalty features on the other.
For more information see the workflow metadata. Find it here: View -> Description
. Calculate loyalty ratio for each customer as the effective # of days till total # of days till now (Feb 1, 2017)
. Calculate total amount of money from contracts and amount of money per year.
